files.project/examples/nested-text.meld:
# Text with Nested Directives

## Basic Example with Add
@text readme = @add "../docs/README.md"

## Example with Run
@text output = @run [../src/script.sh]

## Template Example (without nesting)
@text greeting = [Hello, {{name}}!]

## Show the values
Readme content: {{readme}}
Command output: {{output}}

files.project/examples/nested-data.meld:
# Data with Nested Directives

## Basic Object
@data config = {
  "name": "Sample Project",
  "settings": @add "../config/settings.json",
  "readme": @add "../docs/README.md",
  "scriptOutput": @run [../src/script.sh]
}

## Array Example
@data outputs = [
  @add "../config/settings.json",
  @run [echo "Hello from command!"],
  "Static string item"
]

## Complex Example
@data dashboard = {
  "title": "Project Dashboard",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Configuration",
      "content": @add "../config/settings.json"
    },
    {
      "title": "Command Output",
      "content": @run [../src/script.sh]
    }
  ]
}

## Display some values
Config name: {{config.name}}
First output: {{outputs.0}}
